            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>AVIOT 一向以高性價比的真無線藍牙耳機聞名，這次推出的 WA-Q1 真無線降噪耳機延續此優勢，並號稱全球最細巧的頭戴式降噪耳機，定價僅港幣 599 元。這款耳機具備 55 小時超長續航，還配備混合降噪功能，能有效隔絕外界噪音，讓用家專注享受音樂。以下就由小編帶大家開箱，一睹這款平價實用的入門級耳機真面目吧！</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00220-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00220-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00220.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>糖果色系機身，容易襯衫時尚百搭</h2><p>AVIOT WA-Q1 的外觀設計別具一格，令人眼前一亮。精緻的造型讓人難以聯想到其售價僅為 599 元。耳機外露的連接線加入了復古元素，而多款糖果色選擇則賦予產品青春活力。用家可選擇黑、粉藍、粉紅或灰色，小編測試的是粉紅版本，甜美亮眼，輕易襯託不同穿搭風格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00227-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00227-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00227.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 糖果色系，視覺年輕化</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00224-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00224-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00224.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲外露耳機線，融入復古元素</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00264-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00264-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00264.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲收納時需小心保護電線，避免損壞</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00228-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00228-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00228.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲頭帶刻有「AVIOT」字樣，增添品牌辨識度</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284574" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc002522-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc002522-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc002522.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc002522-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><br /><b>
