        <item>
            <title>騙徒 Deepfake 扮吳君如視像通話森美，稱被賣至柬埔寨需借錢搭船回港</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/31/ai-ng-kwan-yu-video-call-sammy-for-money-scamming/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-ng-kwan-yu-video-call-sammy-for-money-scamming</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/31/ai-ng-kwan-yu-video-call-sammy-for-money-scamming/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 06:40:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Deepfake]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[KK 園區]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[吳君如]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[森美]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[騙案]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1284502</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日森美於 Instagram 上分享了一段趣事，他接到一個自稱「吳君如」的視像電話。電話中的「吳君如」聲稱自己被導演「賣到柬埔寨」，急需向森美借 5,000 元搭船回港。影片迅速引來網民回應，有網民戲謔地問及是否陳可辛導演所為。森美則揭露，這是一場利用 Deepfake 技術進行的電話騙局，並笑稱對方的模樣有六七成像吳君如。</p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEKithpzB5O/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: block; height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 550; line-height: 18px;">在 Instagram 查看這則貼文</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style="width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;"><a style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEKithpzB5O/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sammy Leung 森美（@sammy903）分享的貼文</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//www.instagram.com/embed.js"></script></p><p>森美上傳的影片中，對方的影像與真人相似度頗高，只看外貌確實容易混淆。不過對方濃重的普通話口音成為破綻，令森美迅速識破。影片中的「吳君如」以略顯奇怪的廣東話聲稱：「我係君如，我被導演賣去柬埔寨」，之後問森美「可不可以借 5000 元搭船返香港」。森美不動聲色地追問：「係邊個導演賣咗你過去？」更幽默地提到：「你係咪拍緊《KK 園之戀》？」</p><p>隨後這位假冒的「吳君如」急促地表示，已將銀行户口資料傳送給森美，希望對方立即匯款。森美則將整段通話上載至 Instagram，並特意標註吳君如的官方帳户，幽默地問：「君如，你喺柬埔寨邊度啊？需唔需要揾人救你？」他提醒大家，Deepfake 技術日新月異，若僅憑影像觀察，確實可能受騙。幸而騙徒口音過重，否則有 6、7 成似吳君如。</p><p>森美亦在帖文中感慨，現時電話詐騙手法層出不窮，騙徒甚至利用尖端技術混淆視聽。他呼籲公眾保持警惕，小心 Deepfake 詐騙。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEKithpzB5O/">sammy903@Instagram</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
